%% Diagram: Magic Pocket write path
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BI as Block Index
    participant RT as Repl Table
    participant O as OSDs
    participant CZ as Cross-Zone

    C->>FE: PUT(hash, block)
    FE->>BI: lookup hash
    alt block exists
        BI-->>FE: cell, bucket
        FE-->>C: 200 OK (deduped)
    else new block
        FE->>RT: pick open volume
        RT-->>FE: volume + OSDs
        FE->>O: store to all OSDs
        O-->>FE: fsync ack from each
        FE->>BI: insert mapping
        FE-->>C: 200 OK
        FE-)CZ: enqueue (~1s to second zone)
    end
